Class Stage.Filter

    • com.lightbend.streams.spi.Stage.Filter

    Stage

    public static final class Stage.Filter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Stage.Inlet, Stage.Outlet
    A filter stage.

    The given predicate should be invoked on each element consumed, and if it returns true, the element should be emitted.

    Any RuntimeException thrown by the function should be propagated down the stream as an error.
